General.Name: Ethfinex Nectar Token
General.Description:
The Nectar Token (NEC) is an ERC-20 token that will enpower the Ethfinex, an platform that allows trading ERC-20 compatible tokens. Furthermore, the Ethfinex will feature a community hub for developers, enthusiasts and traders to share and discuss crowdsource information.

NEC will be given for free as loyality points to the token market makers on the Ethfinex exchange.Â On the other hand, the token holders will be able to claim loyalty rewards from the exchange, and advise on the future governance of the platform.
